column5: Wheres everyone headed? I'm stuck casting from shore as I just moved to Kitchener and don't have my canoe down yet. Gonna hit a few spots along the grand. Should be a beauty day for it.
Binbrook crappie derby for me, if I get bored there is also pike and walleye there.
Cook's Bay at sunrise. First time. We'll see what happens!!
Chuck a husky, pause n chill. Nothin like the anticipation of tr next big bite
